Health Check per LB Type

ALB (Application LB):
─────────────────────
Protocol: HTTP / HTTPS
Path    : /health
Checks  : HTTP response code
          200 = healthy ✅
          anything else = unhealthy ❌
Layer   : Layer 7 (reads HTTP)

NLB (Network LB):
──────────────────
Protocol: TCP / HTTP / HTTPS
TCP check: just checks port open
           no HTTP reading
           connection success = healthy ✅
           connection failed  = unhealthy ❌
Layer   : Layer 4 (TCP only)

CLB (Classic LB):
──────────────────
Protocol: HTTP / HTTPS / TCP
older type
not recommended for new setup
